### Current Issue: Database Authentication
The API returns the following error:
```
SQLSTATE[HY000] [1045] Access denied for user 'u542293952_admintest'@'localhost' (using password: YES)
```

**Resolution Steps:**
1. Log in to Hostinger hPanel > Databases.
2. Select database `u542293952_test1`.
3. Reset password for user `u542293952_admintest` to match [.env](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/api/.env) (currently `Admin@1234`) OR update [.env](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/api/.env) with the correct password.
4. Verify by visiting `https://ldmcollege.com/api/health`.

